fried cinnamon powder

00:01:50.955 --> 00:01:52.955
lets start the recipe

00:01:53.220 --> 00:01:55.220
heat just little oil

00:01:56.920 --> 00:02:01.300
whenever you use oil for filling, make sure use little oil

00:02:01.560 --> 00:02:03.560
otherwise your filling will ooze out

00:02:05.620 --> 00:02:10.380
add finely chopped onions

00:02:13.280 --> 00:02:24.360
add pine nuts and on medium or high flame mix it little saute

00:02:26.540 --> 00:02:31.180
add mince

00:02:44.040 --> 00:02:52.960
add salt, crushed black pepper and cinnamon powder

00:02:52.960 --> 00:02:56.820
cook it till meat's water gets dry on medium flame

00:02:57.560 --> 00:03:07.280
your filling is ready, you can see it's a fine fatless mince and cook very fast

00:03:17.900 --> 00:03:23.800
strain all oil with the help of strainer and leave aside to get normal temprature

00:03:43.180 --> 00:03:51.240
now you need a chopper and add bulgur wheat and i strain all water from it

