add roughly chopped onions

00:04:06.338 --> 00:04:09.178
cumin powder

00:04:10.418 --> 00:04:12.418
crushed black pepper

00:04:13.020 --> 00:04:15.020
salt

00:04:15.740 --> 00:04:22.300
here i will tell you, being an Asian we like little spicy.

00:04:22.300 --> 00:04:25.380
you can add little green chillies if you want to

00:04:27.940 --> 00:04:31.080
but traditionally this dish prepare mild

00:04:31.280 --> 00:04:35.640
chop it first then we will add mince into it

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:46.280
chop it well till  it become in smooth paste

00:04:47.780 --> 00:04:49.780
put that into a bowl

00:04:50.340 --> 00:04:54.880
grind the mince to make it smooth

00:04:59.780 --> 00:05:06.980
mix the mince with bulgur wheat very well

00:05:15.120 --> 00:05:26.240
if you think it too soft and you can't handle it , cover it with a cling film and put in the fridge for 10 to 15 minutes

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:37.500
apply some water on your hand because mince won't stick on you hand

00:05:39.000 --> 00:05:42.680
make a small size of ball

00:05:47.220 --> 00:05:49.880
press down with the finger

00:05:50.940 --> 00:05:56.580
and give a shape as a bowl

